latestIgtvVideos.title: Christmas look
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
MERRY CHRISTMAS ✨
a trick to avoid your makeup to cake up is by 
1. moisturize
2. primer
3. setting powder
4. setting spray
5. corrector (optional)
6. foundation
7. concealor
8. contour
9. bake 
10. setting spray
then continue with your normal make-up after.
.
.
.

latestPosts.caption:
Thank you for 300k 🤍
.
I’m so grateful for every single one of you. My life flipped around because you decided to follow me. I went from being homeless, poor, lost in life to finding my purpose in this world. I’m so glad that I get to share this journey of self love and acceptance on this platform. I’m a girl who has literally come from nothing. I come from a broken family and I was left to fend for myself at a very young age. But now I’m able to do so by just being myself on here. Hard work and sticking to your morals and beliefs really does pay off. 

I love you guys so much 🫂
